                  "content": "With all the religions to choose from, it is not possible to tell which one—if any—is true."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "The federal government has the right to intervene when “cults” threaten society."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
